metadata.description:
#1 FARNSWORTH HOUSE | Hanging Architecture

FARNSWORTH HOUSE | Ludwig Mies van der Rohe
This is #1 of the Hanging Architecture collection, for the Houses series. 

In this collection I will try to show you the most important architectural works in the world in a completely new look.
